            <a href="https://members.blossoms.com/login.php">Login</a>
          </p>
          <div class="hero__microproof">
            <span>50+ years of matchmaking</span>
            <span>Verified profiles</span>
            <span>Worldwide community</span>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="shell hero-mobile-copy" aria-label="Hero introduction">
      <div class="hero-mobile-copy__inner">
        <p class="eyebrow">Asian Dating Since 1974</p>
        <h1>Start your journey to something meaningful.</h1>
        <p class="lede">
          Cherry Blossoms is an Asian dating brand for serious connections,
          cultural openness, and a more intentional path to international
          relationships.
        </p>
